item.title: Hello World
item.description: Hey there. Recentlty I started working at JobScore while I was working at my masters degree on Applied Computing. This marked a new stage of my life. One that I am not familiar with, since I just graduated and never worked before. One of my main fears when I started working was stop evolving as a person and as an employee. With that in mind, I took a few commitments with the goal of creating healthy and productive habbits for my new life:
